<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Firewall</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #F2E2CE;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .background-sig {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100vh;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            object-fit: inherit;
            padding-left: 110vh;
            
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #B1B6D3;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .container p {
            color: white;
        }

        button {
            width: 10vh;
            height: 5vh;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background-color: #e088bf;
            border: 2px solid #f777c6;
            color: #000000;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-left: 1vh;
            margin-right: 1vh;
            transform: translateY(110px);
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: rgb(241, 90, 183);
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <img src="./images/deco_sig.svg" alt="fundo_sig" class="background-sig" />
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Firewall</h1>
        <p>Um firewall é uma rede de segurança que monitora e controla o tráfego de rede de entrada e saída com base em regras de segurança predeterminadas.</p>
        <button onclick="window.history.back()">Voltar</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
